        <hr noshade size="2" color="#545A7D">
        
         at the very end, the discussion is about dark elf vs. iksar all the time.<BR>the iksar innate regen is a big advantage but is fairly compensated via the exp penalty, which is meaningless if you have reached Lich Warlock Ophidian)<BR>the darkelf has nice stats, the better int for low/mid lvl, less fac/kos issues and looks pretty nice.</P><P>if you fear to do a mistake, go for one of these.</P><P>eru and gnome, if you like them and like to be different, they are not so bad.</P><P>and yes, humans are a challenge.</P><P>Usul, Warlock</P><P>Just a very last question - "What would you like your tombstone to say?"<a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
