        <hr noshade size="2" color="#545A7D">
        
         basically you asked if making a gnome necro is a mistake, and the answer would be no.  if you are planning on being in a high end guild and doing a lot of raiding, then i would highly suggest you take iksar...the 20% exp penalty can be annoying (i didn't even notice it until 50+) but the regen helps a LOT.  i've had iksar friends pacting DE necro's to keep them alive during AE/curses from certain mobs.</P><P>human is the only class i would say is a mistake to be a necro as.</P><P><a href="http://www.theinverselogic.com/" target="_blank"><BR>Abillister "Monkey" Abu<BR>Inverse Logic</a><a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
