        <hr noshade size="2" color="#545A7D">
        
         Necros really don't get a choice of religion (you cannot be Agnostic, btw).  Only humans really have a choice, and that choice decides your starting city.  Religion has some faction consequences, but nothing you can control.  With the new newbie rules, starting a necro would not be as bad now as when I first started, so go for it...</P><P> <a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
