         If I were in your shoes I would choose an Iksar.  You sound like you want to make the best choice for the end game.  Go Iksar.  </P><P>As Abi said, with Velious and SoL, KOS does not mean much except in the Old World.  And you have little need for the Old World.</P><P>And just start playing the necro.  Why spend time with a warrior?  The new coding for low levels gives you plenty of time to learn the basic mechanics of the game in a low risk environment.</P><P>Just learn early on how to hit the F10 key to change the screens (and hack the eqini file to make the default full screen mode) and use alt+spell_gem_number to cast spells.  Learn some hot keys.  You should be good.</P><P><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=157918" target=new>Ishtarra Gemeinseele </a><BR>Warlock of the Dirty Soul<BR>Uber N00b Extraordinaire<BR>Tunare Server<a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
