         Just because we Gnecro's are not the "beauties" that the DamnedElves are, doesn't make us less worthy.</P><P>There isn't a place we can't get into due to size (one reason I made mine Gnome).<BR>We get tinker, a skill ONLY Gnomes get.<BR>We have decient vision (unlike humans and Erudites).<BR>We have a reasonable INT... which is why people love making Gnome wizards.<BR>And lastly we aren't KoS everywhere.  I can go to Kelethin (spelling for treecity GF?) and Freeport no problems.  Sure the Dwarfs don't like me, but hey, who cares, they taste good.</P><P>If I ever make a new Necro I will be making an Iksar.  But I really have been enjoying my Gnecro as my 2nd char and sometimes consider making her my main, vs my druid.</P><P>Knowledge is only outdone by stupidity.<a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
